# Another thing I noticed

Your container is based on:

```bash
JBOSS_CONTAINER_JAVA_RUN_MODULE
JBOSS_CONTAINER_JAVA_S2I_MODULE
```

This means you're using a Red Hat UBI/S2I Java image.

I have seen cases where S2I injects additional libraries.

Run:

```bash
find /deployments -name "*.jar" 2>/dev/null
```

and

```bash
find /opt -name "*jackson*" 2>/dev/null
```

and

```bash
find /usr -name "jackson*.jar" 2>/dev/null
```

